ncmpy - a [Python + Curses]-based MPD client.

Made by Cyker Way 2011.

Released under GPLv3.

Features:

    Playback control.
    Playlist management.
    Database management.
    Song rating.
    Auto lyrics fetching and saving.
    Lyrics highlighting and OSD.
    Artist-Album view.
    Search by tags in database.
    Vim-like keybinding with single-hand manipulation.

Install:
    
    See INSTALL.

Acknowledgements:

    Lyrics plugin is adapted from ttplyrics: http://code.google.com/p/ttplyrics/
